  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nI tried to debug transaction with ganache-cli but it shows \"1: // No source code found.\"\r\n\r\n## Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n- run ganache-cli with fork of mainnet of etherem\r\n- truffle migrate\r\n- truffle test\r\n- truffle debug <tx_hash>\r\n\r\n## Actual Results\r\n\r\nIt shows \"1: // No source code found.\"\r\nand if i step next(n), the debugging reach to the final step. (Transaction completed successfully.)\r\nIf I make script file and run it, then debug transaction it works correctly, but if I use truffle test, it fails with \"No source code found.\"\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Operating System: Ubuntu 20.02\r\n* Ethereum client: ganache-cli@6.12.2\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): v5.4.7\r\n* node version (`node --version`): v14.16.0\r\n* npm version (`npm --version`): v6.14.11\r\n\r\n",
